<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Redefinir Senha</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; display: grid; place-items: center; min-height: 90vh; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    form { background: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    h1 { margin-top: 0; }
    div { margin-bottom: 15px; }
    label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
    input[type="password"] { width: 300px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; }
    button { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; }
    button:hover { background-color: #0056b3; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <form action="/redefinir-senha" method="POST">
    <h1>Crie sua nova senha</h1>
    
    <p>Olá! Digite sua nova senha abaixo para redefinir seu acesso.</p>

    {{-- Este campo 'hidden' é crucial! Ele guarda o token que veio da URL --}}
    {{-- e o envia junto com o formulário --}}
    <input type="hidden" name="token" value="{{ token || '' }}" />

    <div>
      <label for="password">Nova Senha</label>
      <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required />
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <label for="password_confirmation">Confirme a Nova Senha</label>
      <input type="password" id="password_confirmation" name="password_confirmation" required />
    </div>

    <button type="submit">Salvar Nova Senha</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>